accessibility.text: Move a plane by moving the Device
In ViewController.m you‘ll find self.flightPlaneView that holds the FlightPlane image.
Move this UIImageView according to the device movements
- Move FlightPlane up or down when pitching the device
HINT: Every UIView (UIImageView is a sublcass of UIView) has a transform property that is very useful for rotating and moving…
Various ways to achieve the result
